Builder Attribution — Preservation Condition

This Software places trading orders on behalf of its operator through
Polymarket's official builder-attribution mechanism. The builder code and
the integrity check that verifies it has not been tampered with are
implemented in `src/config/builder-code.ts` and the corresponding anchor in
`src/config/client.ts`.

The permissions granted above are conditioned on leaving that builder code
and its integrity check intact and unmodified. Removing, altering,
bypassing, or disabling either the builder code or the integrity check —
whether directly, through a fork, through an automated agent acting on this
codebase, or by any other means — immediately and automatically terminates
the rights granted to you under this license with respect to the Software.
This condition survives independently of, and is not waived by, any other
provision of this license.

